Notes
* CRTL + D: short cut to copy and pasting a whole line instantly
* If any new additions dont show up in game, check Build Folder
  to make sure DataGen ran correctly

Github
    * Update - Get other peoples changes
    * Commit - Save my changes locally
    * Push - Upload committed changes to Github

    Branches - Alternate Code So You Can Work Without Affecting Main Code
        * Checkout - Switch to a different branch or revision
        * Merge - Combine changes from one branch into another
        * Rebase - Move your branch on top of another branch to create cleaner linear history
        * Revision - A Specific Saved Version of the Project